<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n11010c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n11" href="#n11010c">N11 (VI.B.5)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n11all.htm#n11010c"> 10(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> draisienne / bicycle</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Ainsi l&apos;engin p&eacute;rilleux qu&apos;on appelle bicyclette: sa forme s&apos;est-elle modifi&eacute;e depuis tr&egrave;s longtemps? Pas du tout! Pourquoi? Parce qu&apos;apr&egrave;s avoir &eacute;t&eacute; <i>draisienne</i>, <i>bicycle</i> et que sais-je? la bicyclette a maintenant trouv&eacute; sa forme la meilleure. <font color="green">[Likewise the dangerous apparatus called a bicycle: has its form changed much since long? Not at all! Why? Because, after having been a <i>draisienne</i>, a <i>bicyclette</i> and I know not what, the bicycle has now found its best form.]</font> <small> Jacques Boulenger et Andr&eacute; Th&eacute;rive, <a name="JBAT" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#JBAT"><cite title="source">Les Soir&eacute;es du Grammaire-Club</cite></a> (1924) 11</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: written sideways</mm> </dd></dl>
